ainer to admonition | `:::note\\nContent\\n:::` → `<div class=\"admonition admonition-note\">` |\n| converts :::warning container | `:::warning\\n...\\n:::` → `<div class=\"admonition admonition-warning\">` |\n| converts :::tip container | `:::tip\\n...\\n:::` → `<div class=\"admonition admonition-tip\">` |\n| preserves existing HTML in content | HTML already in content passes through |\n| handles empty content | Empty string returns defined content |\n\n---\n\n#### **Plugin 2: asset-pipeline** (8 tests)\n**Location**: `tests/plugins/asset-pipeline.test.ts`\n**Hook**: `transformContent`\n**Stores**: `ctx.data.set('asset-manifest', { assets: [...] })`\n\n| Test | Requirement |\n|------|------------|\n| rewrites relative image URLs to /assets/ path | `src=\"./image.png\"` → `src=\"/assets/image.png\"` |\n| rewrites relative link URLs to /assets/ path | `href=\"./doc.pdf\"` → `href=\"/assets/doc.pdf\"` |\n| leaves absolute URLs unchanged | `https://...` unchanged |\n| generates asset manifest in ctx.data | Manifest tracks all discovered assets |\n| handles files with no asset references | No error, manifest unchanged |\n| handles multiple assets in one file | All assets found and rewritten |\n| asset manifest includes all discovered assets | Multiple files accumulate in manifest |\n| does not double-process already-rewritten URLs | `/assets/...` not processed again |\n\n---\n\n#### **Plugin 3: syntax-highlight** (9 tests)\n**Location**: `tests/plugins/syntax-highlight.test.ts`\n**Hook**: `transformContent`\n\n| Test | Requirement |\n|------|------------|\n| adds language class to code blocks | `class=\"language-js\"` → `class=\"language-js highlighted\"` |\n| adds data-language attribute to pre tags | `<pre data-language=\"python\">` |\n| handles multiple code blocks in one file | All `<pre><code class=\"language-...\">` processed |\n| handles code block with no language specified | Plain `<code>` blocks unchanged |\n| adds highlighted class to processed blocks | Only 